OL,6,FA civil engineer who was found asleep
OL,7,Fin his work van at a busy roundabout
OL,8,Fin Sussex has been convicted for drink-
OL,9,Fdriving as part of a police campaign.
OL,11,FBenjamin Davies, 34, of Station Road,
OL,12,FHailsham, was found slumped across the
OL,13,Ffront seat of a van at the Rodmill
OL,14,Froundabout in Eastbourne on 2 December.
OL,16,FHe was roused by an officer, following
OL,17,Fa report by the public, and was found
OL,18,Fto be over the alcohol limit.
