OL,6,FHe tested positive for 105
OL,7,Fmicrogrammes (ug) of alcohol per 100
OL,8,Fmillilitres (ml) of breath.
OL,10,FThe legal limit is 35ug of alcohol per
OL,11,F100ml of breath.
OL,13,FDavies admitted being in charge of a
OL,14,Fmotor vehicle while over the legal
OL,15,Falcohol limit.
OL,17,FHe was disqualified for six months and
OL,18,Fwas fined #461, with #85 costs and a
OL,19,F#184 surcharge.
