OL,6,FHead of the Roads Policing Unit (RPU)
OL,7,FSuperintendent, Rachel Glenton, said:
OL,8,F"Those who commit these offences risk
OL,9,Fpunishments which include being
OL,10,Fdisqualified from driving, heavy
OL,11,Ffines, and even the risk of going to
OL,12,Fprison.
OL,14,F"These are nothing compared to the
OL,15,Frisk they pose of causing serious harm
OL,16,For even the death of themselves or
OL,17,Fother road users.
OL,19,F"Drink or drug driving is one of the
OL,20,Fmain causes of people being killed or
OL,21,Fseriously injured on our roads.
