OL,6,F"That is why we continue to urge
OL,7,Fpeople to take steps to prevent drink
OL,8,Fand drug-driving, such as persuading
OL,9,Floved ones not to drive, and taking
OL,10,Fsensible steps such as pre-booking
OL,11,Ftaxis or walking home.
OL,13,F"Our officers are determined to catch
OL,14,Foffenders to help keep our roads safe."
